review_blob: Combination of two of my favorite styles and a very interesting take it is. A one finger head and a light amber color are followed by a smooth and hoppy finish. More to come.
beer_name: Terrapin Side Project Monks Revenge Double IPA

review_blob: Lovely amber color with a one finger head. Strong aroma of caramel and citrus. The acidity and hops are well balanced with the sweetness of the fantastic spring beer
My new favorite IPA. Nothing else necessary. But, it had a golden appearance with a delightfully aromatic one finger head. The taste was perfectly bitter and sweet. Will update.

alcoholic aroma with honey and cherry notes. Dissipating minimal head but vibrant cherry red color. Thick, sweet taste with cherry, honey, and spices. Medium body with sticky texture, lively carbonation and an abrupt finish.
beer_name: Tregs The Mad Elf Holiday Ale
